---
title: Beef in Mushroom Sauce  with scallions and roast potatoes
description: A rich and creamy mushroom sauce covers the succulent beef rump in this recipe that's filled with classic flavours and favoured ingredients.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R09_W43_IE_IECFB30776-6_Main_high-30ae5e1a.jpg
